Package: shinySTRegister
Title: Enables the Alignment of Two Spatial Transcriptomics Samples
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Jonathan", "Sulc", , "jonsulc@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5572-6541"))
Description: Enables the plotting of spatial transcriptomics samples for manual
    alignment. This is done by specifying three corresponding points on each
    sample and then determining the affine transformation from one to the other.
